    • Uses of SalableProduct in products

      Subclasses of SalableProduct in products 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  Armor
      Armor is a child of SalableProduct that has additional integer fields of protection and weight.
      class  Health
      Health is a child of SalableProduct that has the additional integer field of healthRegen that represents how many health points are recovered when this item is used by player.
      class  Weapon
      Weapon is a child of SalableProduct that has additional integer field dmg that represents how many hitpoints are dealt to an enemy when struck by this weapon.
